644
00:42:25,058 --> 00:42:28,359
Expert Ning is very illustrious! Hero, you've never heard of him?

645
00:42:28,359 --> 00:42:32,978
Expert Ning is a legendary figure who lives on Mount Dianzu!

646
00:42:32,978 --> 00:42:35,380
